OL,3,CAll you need to know about this year's
OL,4,CBadminton Horse Trials
OL,6,FThe 78th Badminton Horse Trials got
OL,7,Funder way today in South
OL,8,FGloucestershire.
OL,10,FThe five-day event, which takes place
OL,11,Fon The Duke of Beaufort's estate, is
OL,12,Frunning from 6-10 May and is described
OL,13,Fas the "triathlon" of the equine world.
OL,15,FThe event is expected to attract
OL,16,Faround 200,000 spectators over the
OL,17,Ffive days.
OL,19,FWhat is the Badminton Horse Trials?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
