OL,3,CAll you need to know about this year's
OL,4,CBadminton Horse Trials
OL,6,FBadminton Horse Trails was founded in
OL,7,F1949 and is recognised as a five-star
OL,8,Finternational competition, only seven
OL,9,Fsuch events in the world.
OL,11,FIt aims to showcase the very best of
OL,12,Fhorsemanship with a line-up of
OL,13,Fdisplays during the competition, which
OL,14,Fboasts a #125,000 prize pot.
OL,16,FWhat's happening and when?
OL,18,FLeMieux Grassroots Championships
OL,20,FInternational Event
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
