OL,3,CAll you need to know about this year's
OL,4,CBadminton Horse Trials
OL,6,FWho to expect?
OL,8,FOlympic medallists, World and European
OL,9,FChampions and 15 of the world's top 20
OL,10,Franked riders will be at this year's
OL,11,FBadminton Horse Trials.
OL,13,FHarry Meade, who is the world number
OL,14,Fone, Olympic gold medallist Laura
OL,15,FCollett and last year's runner up
OL,16,FOliver Townend will be in attendance.
OL,18,FHer Majesty The Queen will also be at
OL,19,Fthe event on Friday in her role as
OL,20,FPatron of the Ebony Horse Club, the
OL,21,Fevent's chosen charity this year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
