OL,3,CAll you need to know about this year's
OL,4,CBadminton Horse Trials
OL,6,FAlthough the main focus of the event
OL,7,Fis the horses, event director Jane
OL,8,FTuckwell says it doesn't matter if you
OL,9,Flike them or not.
OL,11,F"It's a wonderful day in the country,
OL,12,Fyou can go for a wonderful walk round
OL,13,Fthe beautiful badminton park and then
OL,14,Fif you do like horses, you can see the
OL,15,Fbest horses doing what they do best."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
